{"tid":449637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電動輪椅男現身紅磡漆咸道北，DIY倒後鏡快線飛馳","createTime":"2017-10-27T10:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T12:35:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb625b182f567cdcf46c76944929bddbad1ff04","tid":449637,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171027/large/1509091591_0056.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171027%2Flarge%2F1509091591_0056.jpg&h=27e349a8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n讀者趙小姐於下午1時48分左右，看到一名男子坐着電動輪椅，沿漆咸道北往觀塘方向行駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。其間輪椅漢由三線切到快線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其他車輛都紛紛減速或停下讓路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。其實於去年1月中，也有駕駛者拍攝到有電動輪椅在漆咸道北行駛﹝ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1ZiUt3k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1ZiUt3k&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=80d1ee0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1ZiUt3k</a> ﹞，輪椅及輪椅漢的外形，與今日被拍攝到的極為相似，不排除有人不顧安全，繼續駕乘電動輪椅駛上馬路。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171027/large/1509091899_6b1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171027%2Flarge%2F1509091899_6b1f.jpg&h=dc70d635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171027/57383986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F57383986&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=c6a93c57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F57383986&h=010eef5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171027/57383986</a></div>"},{"pid":"73d31b351be15deffdbc5b8b89ddc37ea2d5e35c","tid":449637,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03703d5ed7a45bc7dcffc3f72088e34138dc14a5","tid":449637,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"讀者趙小姐的車cam拍攝到，今日下午1時48分，她的私家車沿漆咸道北往觀塘行駛，至理工對開，赫見前面左三線有一輪電動輪椅，其他車輛都停下或減速讓路；電動輪椅繼續前行，甚至切出快線行駛。趙說：「初時見到前面一堆車停低，睇睇下竟然係架電動輪椅，其他車都要避佢。」她又說：「唔可以咁樣，輪椅上個人用化妝鏡當倒後鏡，好危險呀！如果佢有車牌，應該告佢，告佢危險駕駛，冇頭盔又冇安全帶。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171027/large/1509091085_fb68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171027%2Flarge%2F1509091085_fb68.jpg&h=483f1326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 輪椅漢以圓形鏡子當倒後鏡。</span></div>"},{"pid":"f667d1e06f84137b69400e522f880e809ffb83c3","tid":449637,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"鬼唔望佢俾車撞死"},{"pid":"03ffa813e82ac647d30c715c8e3b86c5247fa944","tid":449637,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b79132dc8555c9c4f29fb3616acc26c7f9d97cdd","tid":449637,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171027/large/1509094030_69ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171027%2Flarge%2F1509094030_69ca.jpg&h=2b970a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 電動輪椅在馬路上穿梭，險象環生。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，電動輪椅屬醫療助行器，不屬於車輛，不能在馬路上行駛；任何人士若在公眾地方罔顧後果或疏忽地使用電動輪椅，或其速度或使用方式會對公眾產生危險，可能違反《簡易程序治罪條例》的規定。根據《簡易程序治罪條例》，違例者可被判處罰款5,000元或監禁3個月。"},{"pid":"6a41de8a6f3c8e27f6f10bcdea9b0a51196df8c8","tid":449637,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"John English!!"},{"pid":"a4e598ab8da39ecef147f463992d123a185b5781","tid":449637,"uid":1167,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:01:34.000Z","msg":"死唔去仲係到獻世，唔好出黎累人累物啦。希望佢病痛足一世。<br />\n歡迎口德撚挑戰"},{"pid":"8c97403826e8cc1dedfb54dd09dc6a1960310db3","tid":449637,"uid":14250,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"如果架車夠快其實幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b515b0ccd0cce44ee29266a778d711729d18fb1","tid":449637,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"醫生紙做車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bf8b4d2a78b440b03e087e72af08ffb0a1f919","tid":449637,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/PUdZikUaG_M/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FPUdZikUaG_M%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f6611685&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48245749dcd435ef2bd881dd2f4450530563c6ec","tid":449637,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"Old news is so"},{"pid":"6c3ce9e584fd93d8b4b4aedaf92fee5374fd6d4f","tid":449637,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Old news is so</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=e3feda93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?